Lisp:reverse-every-other-line.el  --- A mode for genuine bidirectional reading of text by reversing every other line in the visible buffer part.  Depends on program convert of the ImageMagic-suite.

Git repo at https://github.com/marcowahl/reverse-every-other-line

Comments and improvements welcome.


